Package agh.alleviation.model

Class Movie

java.lang.Object
agh.alleviation.model.EntityObject
agh.alleviation.model.Movie
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Externalizable, java.io.Serializable
@Entity
public class Movie
extends EntityObject
This class is responsible for storing information about movies. It stores the name of the movie, its genre, director and a short list of actors. Actors are kept in a coma separated String. MovieService will be responsible for processing this list into a useful structure.
Author:
Kamil Krzempek, Anna Nosek
See Also:
Genre, Serialized Form
